And we were walking
across the desert

00:28:40.260 --> 00:28:42.270 align:middle line:84%
and suddenly you
turn left or right

00:28:42.270 --> 00:28:44.640 align:middle line:84%
because you can
hear the song that's

00:28:44.640 --> 00:28:47.760 align:middle line:84%
memorialized in these
magnetic strips of tape

00:28:47.760 --> 00:28:48.880 align:middle line:90%
along the landscape.

